The frequency of each moderate activity per week was multiplied by the duration of the activity, and then the product was mul . . . Yes

It was created by assigning a value of 4 to reported transportation activity. The frequency of transportation activity per week was multiplied by the duration of the activity, and then th . . . Yes
PAQ MET_VIG MET_MINUTES SCORE PER WEEK FOR VIGOROUS ACTIVITY This is the MET_Minutes score per week for vigorous activity. It was created by assigning a value of 8 to each vigorous activity. The frequency of each vigorous activity per week was multiplied by the duration of the activity, and then the product was mul . . . Yes
